  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 47,
      "chapterTitle": "一二 人类的代价",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "22781919_20_1824-2119",
          "range": "2390-2685",
          "rangeStart": 2390,
          "rangeEnd": 2685,
          "markText": "这一问题对我们每个人来说，正如同对密歇根州的知更鸟或对米拉米奇的鲑鱼一样，是一个互相联系、互相依赖的生态学问题。我们毒杀了一条河流上的讨厌的飞虫，于是鲑鱼就逐渐衰弱和死亡；我们毒死了湖中的蚊蚋，于是这些毒物就在食物链中由一环进入另一环，湖滨的鸟儿很快就变成了毒物的牺牲品；我们向榆树喷了药，于是在随后来临的那个春天里就再也听不到知更鸟的歌声了，这不是因为我们直接向知更鸟喷了药，而是因为这种毒物通过我们现在已熟知的榆树叶—蚯蚓—知更鸟一步步地得以转移。上述这些事故是记录在案的、可以观察到的，它们是我们周围可见世界的一部分。它们反映出了生命或死亡的联系之网，科学家们把它们作为生态学来研究。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1676787377,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-02-19 14:16:17",
          "chapterUid": 47,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22781919&chapterUid=47&rangeStart=2390&rangeEnd=2685",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5d732430715b9fdf5d75eb6?chapterUid=47&rangeStart=2390&rangeEnd=2685"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22781919_31_632-730",
      "chapterUid": 31,
      "range": "632-730",
      "markText": "我对人类感到悲观，因为它对于自己的利益太过精明。我们对待自然的办法是打击并使之屈服。如果我们不是这样的多疑和专横，如果我们能调整好与这颗行星的关系，并深怀感激之心对待它，我们本可有更好的存活机会。",
      "totalCount": 1380,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22781919&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=632&rangeEnd=730",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5d732430715b9fdf5d75eb6?chapterUid=31&rangeStart=632&rangeEnd=730"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22781919_30_521-550",
      "chapterUid": 30,
      "range": "521-550",
      "markText": "人类已经失去预见和自制能力，人类自身将摧毁地球并随之而灭亡",
      "totalCount": 1111,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22781919&chapterUid=30&rangeStart=521&rangeEnd=550",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5d732430715b9fdf5d75eb6?chapterUid=30&rangeStart=521&rangeEnd=550"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22781919_37_1812-1830",
      "chapterUid": 37,
      "range": "1812-1830",
      "markText": "人们恰恰很难辨认自己创造出来的魔鬼。",
      "totalCount": 896,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22781919&chapterUid=37&rangeStart=1812&rangeEnd=1830",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5d732430715b9fdf5d75eb6?chapterUid=37&rangeStart=1812&rangeEnd=1830"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22781919_33_3870-3895",
      "chapterUid": 33,
      "range": "3870-3895",
      "markText": "任何一处食物链中毒最终将导致所有地方的食物链中毒。",
      "totalCount": 880,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22781919&chapterUid=33&rangeStart=3870&rangeEnd=3895",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5d732430715b9fdf5d75eb6?chapterUid=33&rangeStart=3870&rangeEnd=3895"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22781919_42_11733-11784",
      "chapterUid": 42,
      "range": "11733-11784",
      "markText": "居然能默认对活生生的生命采取这样使其受苦的行动，作为人类，我们中间有哪一个不曾降低了我们做人的身份呢？",
      "totalCount": 714,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22781919&chapterUid=42&rangeStart=11733&rangeEnd=11784",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5d732430715b9fdf5d75eb6?chapterUid=42&rangeStart=11733&rangeEnd=11784"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22781919_38_15469-15532",
      "chapterUid": 38,
      "range": "15469-15532",
      "markText": "到目前看来，尚未有人提出过这样的建议——做人的内吸杀虫试验，它将使得我们（体内的毒性）致蚊子于死地。也许这就是下一步的工作了。",
      "totalCount": 636,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22781919&chapterUid=38&rangeStart=15469&rangeEnd=15532",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5d732430715b9fdf5d75eb6?chapterUid=38&rangeStart=15469&rangeEnd=15532"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22781919_33_4897-4928",
      "chapterUid": 33,
      "range": "4897-4928",
      "markText": "现在的体制是浮士德式的交易——以长远悲剧的代价来换取近期利益。",
      "totalCount": 630,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22781919&chapterUid=33&rangeStart=4897&rangeEnd=4928",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5d732430715b9fdf5d75eb6?chapterUid=33&rangeStart=4897&rangeEnd=4928"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22781919_37_6958-6985",
      "chapterUid": 37,
      "range": "6958-6985",
      "markText": "让·罗斯唐说：“我们既然忍受了，就应该有知情的权利。”",
      "totalCount": 630,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22781919&chapterUid=37&rangeStart=6958&rangeEnd=6985",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5d732430715b9fdf5d75eb6?chapterUid=37&rangeStart=6958&rangeEnd=6985"
    },
